{"tid":2120774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田區疫症爆發真相","createTime":"2020-07-23T01:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T03:04:48.000Z","uid":105567,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"18f46609afbd5c3497934140768b4847ce9888b1","tid":2120774,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"絕密相片曝光 請大量廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQhttcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQhttcp.jpg&h=95dd09e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n500人室內零距離<br />\n除罩唱歌影相零防疫<br />\n<br />\n香港太公報：<br />\n<br />\n有一群自稱KOL在7月6日於沙田聚集500人，室內互動活動，零社交距離，相片中可見不少人沒有戴口罩，活動後各人返回自己社區。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衛生局前局長高永文日前接受訪問時指出，新冠病毒潛伏期多數在四至七天，然後認為大爆發同7月1日的示威日期「吻合」。<br />\n<br />\n不如高醫生comment一下報道中7月6日成500人室內近距離活動，同工聯會7月2日黃大仙大型慶回歸無罩活動，時間上又同大爆發「吻合」嗎？唔係潛水嘛？<br />\n<br />\n歡迎報料香港太公報！<br />\n香港姜太公，<br />\n有事必報！<br />\n<br />\n#高永文 #何君堯 #李梓敬"},{"pid":"01d394570f44b0ac2ca3c442e4e5197d813c3cca","tid":2120774,"uid":1646,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:49:45.000Z","msg":"藍絲不會報導既真相！"},{"pid":"603c29341c7e54d30813dcd6e9862852b1c3d5b7","tid":2120774,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dba344fb0a106d67129af6c6a2985206af8433","tid":2120774,"uid":13689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"